== Welcome to DoTranslation v0.1

This utility translate a yaml file into another yaml file using google translator

It keeps the same hierarchy as the in yml file.
All texts not translated are prefixed with "NT - "

Command line is:

ruby do_translation.rb file.yml lg_dest

The source language is the one defined in the first line of the source yaml file as shown below:

en:
  item1 : "text one"
  ...

